+import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
+
+class Tablee extends StatelessWidget {
+  const Tablee({Key? key}) : super(key: key);
+
+  @override
+  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
+    return MaterialApp(
+      home: Scaffold(
+        appBar: AppBar(
+          title: const Text('Table Example'),
+        ),
+        body: Center(
+          child: Padding(
+            padding: const EdgeInsets.all(8.0),
+            child: Table(
+              border: TableBorder.all(),
+              children: [
+                TableRow(
+                  children: [
+                    TableCell(
+                      child: Container(
+                        color: Colors.grey,
+                        child: const SizedBox(
+                          height: 50,
+                          child: Center(
+                            child: Text('BMI'),
+                          ),
+                        ),
+                      ),
+                    ),
+                    TableCell(
+                      child: Container(
+                        color: Colors.grey,
+                        child: const SizedBox(
+                          height: 50,
+                          child: Center(
+                            child: Text(
+                              'Status',
+                              style: TextStyle(
+24                            ),
+                          ),
+                        ),
+                      ),
+                    ),
+                  ],
+                ),
+                TableRow(
+                  children: [
+                    TableCell(
+                      child: Container(
+                        color: Colors.red,
+                        child: const Center(
+                          child: Text('Row 2, Column 1'),
+                        ),
+                      ),
+                    ),
+                    TableCell(
+                      child: Container(
+                        color: Colors.yellow,
+                        child: const Center(
+                          child: Text('Row 2, Column 2'),
+                        ),
+                      ),
+                    ),
+                  ],
+                ),
+                // Add more TableRows for additional rows
+              ],
+            ),
+          ),
+        ),
+      ),
+    );
+  }
+}
